anApp BuildTool Set Up
======================

1. Be sure that the following are installed:
   * Phing -- http://phing.info/docs/guide/current/chapters/Setup.html
   * PHPUnit -- http://www.phpunit.de/manual/current/en/installation.html
   * Git -- http://git-scm.com/
2. Edit build.properties and set variables as per your local environment.


Building a new project
======================
In the buildTool directory, simply type:

phing

And you will be asked a series of questions about your new
project. After answering these questions, you will have a brand
spanking new anApp project all set up for you.